(262, 1, '2016-10-19 08:50:21', '2016-10-19 08:50:21', '<h4>Project Location</h4>            \n<p class="text">Maniyakarampalayam, Ganapathy, Coimbatore Spacious 2 BHK – Rs. 39.1 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price) Spacious 3 BHK – Rs. 48.66 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price)</p>					\n<h4>Project Location</h4>            \n<p class="text">Maniyakarampalayam, Ganapathy, Coimbatore Spacious 2 BHK – Rs. 39.1 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price) Spacious 3 BHK – Rs. 48.66 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price)</p>					\n<h4>Project Location</h4>            \n<p class="text">Maniyakarampalayam, Ganapathy, Coimbatore Spacious 2 BHK – Rs. 39.1 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price) Spacious 3 BHK – Rs. 48.66 Lakhs (All Inclusive Price)</p>					\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>About Archon</strong></h2>\n<h2></h2>\n<p>Located in the technological hub of Bangalore, Archon Consulting is a privately-owned IT Infrastructure services company. Incorporated in 2010, Archon Consulting is committed to delivering value-based solutions &amp; services that positively impact business efficiency.</p>\n<p>We offer customized, high-quality, ROI-driven IT Infrastructure Solutions. Our customized end-to-end on-time solutions facilitate optimum management of your technology investments and resources.</p>\n<p>Armed with extensive industry knowledge across verticals, our skilled team of experts offer optimum solutions after an in-depth comprehensive analysis of individual client requirements. Our services and solutions are tailor-made for businesses across diverse industries.</p><p><img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-67" src="http://localhost/ArchonPort/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/banner2-1024x576.jpg" alt="banner2" width="720" height="405"></p><h3 class="widget-title">Testimonials</h3><blockquote><p>We are looking for high-performing individuals who would never settle for being anything but the best at what they do. We work hard, play hard, enjoy the journey</p><p>We offer customized, high-quality, ROI-driven IT Infrastructure Solutions. Our customized end-to-end on-time solutions facilitate optimum management of your technology investments and resources.</p><p>Armed with extensive industry knowledge across verticals, our skilled team of experts offer optimum solutions after an in-depth comprehensive analysis of individual client requirements.</p></blockquote><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Model House</span></h1>&nbsp;<h2 style="text-align: center;">Contact Details</h2><center><strong><em>NITHYA GARDENS</em></strong></center><p>&nbsp;</p><center>528/1A, Sankarlingam Road, Maniyakarampalayam, Ganapathy Village,</center><p>&nbsp;</p><center>Coimbatore -06. Website :www.nithyaestates.com</center>&nbsp;', 'Home Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-10-19 08:50:21', '2016-10-19 08:50:21', '', 76, 'http://localhost/ArchonPort/76-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
